        <p>GreenShift is one of my current projects, I started development on it for my dissertation and i've continued to work on it in my free-time after submission. It was online under this domain <a href="https://greenshift.azurewebsites.net/">GreenShift</a> but I have since taken it offline so I can work on it more before releasing it under a custom domain. I have also made an Android mobile app for GreenShift</p>
        <p> The idea behind GreenShift is that most people understand that global warming is an issue but they don't understand how significant their personal lifestyles are in CO2 contribution, GreenShifts goal is to slowly educate its users via gamification and passive facts into better undertsanding their environmental impact</p>
