        <p>This is a tool I made with Python using Tkinter and the OpenAI API. I was struggling in interviews and didn't want to be paying the prices that some services offer for interview simulation. This project taught me a lot about how LLM's work and how difficult it can be to get them to do what you want them to do. The logic behind the program is relatively simple, but this project was time consuming because I spent days soley refining 4.1 mini's outputs to be what I'd consider a realistic interview experience.</p>
